%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Circle'%20used%20an%20AI%20player%20to%20create%20a%20bot%20witch%20hunt%20%E2%80%94%20and%20soon%2C%20we%20might%20all%20be%20defending%20our%20humanity%20online%20too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20computer%20tower%20with%20blue%20and%20pink%20lights%20from%20the%20circle%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20stool%20in%20front%20of%20a%20pink%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66340ee2ec0c696569009402%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMax%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20is%20an%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20he%20can't%20play%20with%20the%20best%20of%20them.%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMax%20is%20the%20first%20AI%20contestant%20on%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20literally%20a%20chatbot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMax%20is%20pretty%20boring%2C%20but%20having%20an%20AI%20in%20the%20game%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20robot%20witch%20hunt.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnfortunately%20for%20us%2C%20this%20sort%20of%20thing%20is%20already%20starting%20to%20happen%20in%20real%20life%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-to-film-the-circle-behind-the-scenes-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20tends%20to%20lean%20more%20asinine%20than%20Asimov%20%E2%80%94%20but%20including%20an%20AI%20player%20who%20can%20chat%20it%20up%20with%20the%20best%20of%20them%20is%20the%20most%20science%20fiction%20twist%20the%20game%20has%20pulled%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20a%20British%20import%20that%20Netflix%20launched%20in%202020%2C%20is%20ostensibly%20a%20commentary%20on%20social%20media.%20Players%20can%20only%20interact%20with%20each%20other%20through%20a%20chat%20interface%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20can%20present%20themselves%20in%20whichever%20way%20they'd%20like%20as%20they%20scheme%20their%20way%20to%20becoming%20the%20most%20popular%20player%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20game%20and%20winning%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20feels%20like%20little%20more%20than%20a%20competition%20(albeit%20a%20rather%20entertaining%20one).%20But%20bringing%20an%20AI%20player%20into%20the%20mix%20reflects%20some%20of%20the%20future%20online%20trials%20we're%20likely%20to%20face%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20some%20that%20are%20already%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22laruen%20on%20the%20circle%20wearing%20a%20black%20dress%20with%20puffy%20sleeves%2C%20her%20hair%20worn%20curly%20and%20up%20in%20two%20small%20ponytails%2C%20she's%20smiling%20widely%20and%20has%20her%20hands%20up%20near%20her%20face%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66355c760dfb1341e9029f9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPoor%20Lauren%20doesn't%20realize%20that%20she's%20become%20besties%20with%20a%20chatbot%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Circle's%26quot%3B%20AI%20player%20is%20Max%2C%20a%20chatbot%20masquerading%20as%20a%2026-year-old%20veterinary%20intern%20from%20Wisconsin%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Banimal%20whisperer%20with%20a%20knack%20for%20making%20bad%20pottery%2C%20no%20cap.%26quot%3B%20He's%20got%20a%20nice%20face%20(courtesy%20of%20comedian%20Griffin%20James%2C%20who's%20being%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6IQWbmLilc%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20good%20sport%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20a%20cute%20dog%20named%20Pippa.%20If%20all%20of%20that%20isn't%20enough%20to%20clue%20you%20in%2C%20he's%20boring%20and%20safe%20as%20hell.%20And%20when%20the%20other%20players%20learn%20that%20there's%20a%20bot%20in%20their%20midst%20(without%20knowing%20who)%2C%20they%20don't%20turn%20on%20him.%20They%20turn%20on%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20ratchets%20up%20the%20tension%20through%20challenges%20that%20require%20players%20to%20rank%20each%20other%20on%20a%20scale%20from%20most%20to%20least%20human%20or%20prove%20their%20humanity%20by%20uploading%20photos%20of%20moments%20when%20they%20felt%20%26quot%3Balive.%26quot%3B%20Messy%20accusations%20ensue%2C%20which%2035-year-old%20podcaster%20Steffi%20takes%20the%20brunt%20of%20after%20proving%20that%20she%20has%20an%20encyclopedic%20knowledge%20of%20astrology%20(these%20people%20don't%20have%20any%20friends%20who%20can%20provide%20horoscopes%20on%20demand%3F).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Contestant%20Stephanie%20%26quot%3BSteffi%26quot%3B%20Hill%20in%20season%20six%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66218f1810c6b0cde5f0f1af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContestant%20Stephanie%20%26quot%3BSteffi%26quot%3B%20Hill%20in%20season%20six%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20Max's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20game%20says%20much%20more%20about%20us%20as%20humans%20than%20the%20current%20capabilities%20of%20chatbots%2C%20though%20he%20performs%20admirably.%20The%20players%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20react%20viscerally%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20threatened%20by%20a%20bot%20and%20even%20more%20viscerally%20to%20accusations%20that%20they%20are%20one.%20And%20unfortunately%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20stuff%20is%20already%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20rise%20of%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20which%20was%20created%20by%20OpenAI%2C%20people%20have%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20students%20using%20it%20to%20cheat%20on%20their%20classwork%20by%20making%20it%20write%20essays%20or%20do%20research%20for%20them.%20Look%20at%20this%20wild%20graph%20my%20colleague%20Alistair%20Barr%20published%20last%20September%20that%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschool-is-back-chatgpt-mainly-tool-cheating-homework-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esearch%20interest%20in%20ChatGPT%20plummeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20summer%20when%20students%20were%20out%20of%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversities-ditch-ai-detectors-over-fears-students-falsely-accused-cheating-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20schools%20have%20eschewed%20AI%20detectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20OpenAI%20itself%20has%20said%20could%20be%20faulty%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0because%20they%20may%20lead%20to%20false%20accusations%20that%20students%20used%20chatbots%20to%20complete%20their%20work.%20Look%20at%20this%20guide%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2023%2F08%2F14%2Fprove-false-positive-ai-detection-turnitin-gptzero%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Pos%3C%2Fa%3Et%20published%20in%20August%202023%20about%20what%20to%20do%20if%20you're%20accused%20of%20using%20AI%20to%20cheat!%20Folks%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Ftech%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2Fdating-app-bots-learn-how-spot-them-before-swiping%2F5406539002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworried%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20stealth%20chatbots%20on%20dating%20apps%20like%20Tinder%20for%20years.%20And%20as%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20social%20media%20is%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-flooded-spammy-ai-content-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20rife%20with%20spammy%20AI-generated%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20reliant%20on%20ChatGPT.%20Hell%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20opt-in%20to%20chatbot%20relationships%2C%20you%20can%20do%20what%20my%20colleague%20Katie%20Notopoulos%20did%20and%20go%20on%20dates%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FluS49hGppxk%3Fsi%3DTiXfh4XJIOUzSlH0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20really%20here%20to%20litigate%20how%20AI%20language%20learning%20models%20are%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt4-openai-ai-models-dont-improve-over-time-dumber-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20or%20less%20sophisticated%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20more%20human.%20But%20what%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%26quot%3B%20shows%20is%20that%20their%20simple%20presence%2C%20and%20potential%20for%20deception%2C%20puts%20all%20of%20us%20under%20the%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20show%20is%20an%20extreme%20environment%3A%20Players%20don't%20meet%20each%20other%20face%20to%20face%2C%20and%20they%20interact%20in%20fairly%20limited%20ways%20within%20the%20parameters%20of%20a%20specific%20game.%20Max%20was%20able%20to%20study%20past%20seasons%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Circle%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20bot's%20narration%20in%20the%20show%2C%20and%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20didn't%20behave%20more%20bizarrely%20than%20any%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20real%20world%2C%20we%20can%20use%20further%20context%20clues%20to%20evaluate%20the%20humanity%20of%20those%20we%20interact%20with%20online.%20Do%20they%20have%20a%20new%20acc