0in%201977%20when%20it%20was%20still%20a%20cow%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeth%20Ann%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20ended%20up%20in%20Colorado%20because%20of%20Eric.%20We%20did%20long-distance%20dating%20between%20Kansas%20City%20and%20Denver.%20When%20we%20got%20married%20in%201996%2C%20I%20moved%20with%20him%20to%20the%20Denver%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEric%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe're%20both%20full-time%20realtors%20with%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20HomeServices.%20We%20bought%20some%20investment%20properties%20in%20Denver%2C%20and%20in%202009%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2F1031-exchange%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1031-exchanged%3C%2Fa%3E%20three%20of%20those%20properties%20for%20a%20place%20in%20Thousand%20Oaks.%20So%2C%20we've%20actually%20owned%20our%20current%20home%20here%20in%20California%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeth%20Ann%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20planned%20on%20getting%20to%20California%20at%20some%20point.%20But%20it%20took%20us%20about%2014%20years%20to%20see%20that%20come%20into%20being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDenver%20used%20to%20be%20a%20great%20place%20to%20raise%20a%20family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEric%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EColorado%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20places%20to%20legalize%20recreational%20marijuana%2C%20which%20we%20did%20not%20vote%20for.%20In%20our%20opinion%2C%20that's%20when%20things%20started%20turning%20in%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubi-cash-payments-reduced-homelessness-increased-employment-denver-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeless%3C%2Fa%3E%20population%20in%20Denver%20is%20pretty%20insane%2C%20even%20in%20the%20suburbs.%20It%20really%20started%20to%20affect%20our%20quality%20of%20life.%20We%20started%20feeling%20uncomfortable%20going%20downtown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20got%20really%20bad%2C%20too.%20Twenty%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20much%20easier%20to%20go%20up%20to%20the%20mountains%20and%20ski%20for%20a%20day.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20traffic%20is%20just%20hideous.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisappointing-photos-show-skiing-in-colorado-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eski%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'd%20better%20be%20willing%20to%20get%20up%20at%205%20a.m.%20and%20not%20get%20home%20until%208%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20liked%20to%20take%20cruise%20vacations%20to%20escape%20Denver%20during%20the%20winter.%20Over%20time%2C%20we%20realized%20we%20are%20more%20ocean%20people%20than%20mountain%20people.%20We%20just%20got%20sick%20and%20tired%20of%20the%20snow%20in%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Eric%20and%20Beth%20Ann%20Mott's%20car%20covered%20in%20snow%20in%20Colorado%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6635600eec0c696569011301%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEric%20and%20Beth%20Ann%20said%20they%20got%20tired%20of%20dealing%20with%20Denver's%20constant%20snow.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Eric%20and%20Beth%20Ann%20Mott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20really%20a%20combination%20of%20different%20things%20that%20changed%20the%20environment.%20It's%20just%20not%20what%20we%20used%20to%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeth%20Ann%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20first%20started%20considering%20a%20move%20to%20California%20during%20COVID%20when%20we%20were%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20couldn't%20go%20anywhere.%20We%20had%20always%20talked%20about%20ending%20up%20in%20California%20someday%2C%20and%20we%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20someday%20be%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECOVID%20also%20forced%20everyone%20to%20do%20things%20remotely.%20We%20started%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20client%20appointments%20via%20Zoom.%20So%2C%20the%20seed%20of