-tanker-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeadly%20crashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20737%20Max%20planes%20in%202018%20and%202019%2C%20Fehrm%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-investigating-potentially-catastrophic-boeing-spaceship-error-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENASA%2C%20too%2C%20investigated%20Boeing's%20company%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20error-ridden%202019%20Starliner%20test%20flight.%20Doug%20Loverro%2C%20a%20NASA%20associate%20administrator%20overseeing%20the%20program%20at%20the%20time%2C%20said%20that%20the%20two%20deadly%20737%20Max%20crashes%20were%20on%20his%20mind%20when%20he%20launched%20that%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ethiopian%20airlines%20boeing%20737%20max%20crash%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ca70edbc6cc506b3a25a524%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEthiopian%20police%20officers%20walk%20past%20the%20debris%20of%20the%20Ethiopian%20Airlines%20Flight%20ET%20302%20plane%20crash.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBaz%20Ratner%2FFile%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20those%20disasters%2C%20Boeing%20hired%20a%20new%20CEO%20and%20board%20members%20with%20engineering%20backgrounds%20and%20established%20an%20Aerospace%20Safety%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20were%20definitely%20improvements%2C%20Fehrm%20said%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20change%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-might-kill-middle-management-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiddle%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20filtered%20up%20by%20embracing%20KPIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20desire%20to%20get%20the%20production%20rate%20up%20to%20the%20max%20is%20still%20there%2C%20and%20the%20old%20habits%20of%20cutting%20some%20corners%20in%20order%20to%20shape%20numbers%20are%20still%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Fehrm%