called%20the%20Icefall%20Doctors%2C%20and%20this%20year%2C%20they%20delayed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmount-everest-trash-crowds-climbers-edmund-hillary-sherpa-team-member-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEverest's%20climbing%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2012%20days%20due%20to%20unsafe%20conditions%20on%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20will%20only%20become%20more%20dangerous%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmount-everest-base-camp-to-move-due-to-climate-change-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20temperatures%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Paul%20Mayewski%2C%20Mount%20Everest%20researcher%20and%20climatologist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maine%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20studies%20how%20climate%20change%20is%20affecting%20the%20highest%20peaks%20on%20our%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20makes%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20so%20dangerous%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20climber%20scales%20a%20ladder%20in%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663538d8ec0c69656900ff35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeep%20crevasses%20and%20deadly%20avalanches%20make%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefalls%20one%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%2C%20and%20dangerous%20passages%20to%20summiting%20Everest.%3Cp%3EOlaf%20Rieck%2FWikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20is%20essentially%20a%20slow-moving%20river%20of%20ice%20that%20gradually%20falls%20down%20the%20mountain%20as%20the%20Khumbu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmelting-glaciers-ice-sheets-sea-level-rise-climate-disaster-2022-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Columbia%2520Glacier%2520in%2520Alaska%2Ctold%2520Insider%2520in%2520an%2520email.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlacier%20recedes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20movement%20is%20what%20makes%20it%20so%20unstable%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20deep%20crevasses%20and%20deadly%20avalanches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%201953%20and%202019%2C%2045%20people%20lost%20their%20lives%20on%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall.%20The%20three%20major%20causes%20of%20death%20were%20avalanches%20onto%20the%20icefall%20(49%25%20of%20deaths)%2C%20icefall%20collapse%20(33%25)%2C%20and%20falling%20into%20a%20crevasse%20(13%25)%2C%20according%20to%20Alan%20Arnette%2C%20a%20Mount%20Everest%20summiter%20and%20climbing%20coach%20who%20writes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alanarnette.com%2Fblog%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20each%20climbing%20season%2C%20the%20Icefall%20Doctors%20are%20the%20first%20to%20traverse%20this%20treacherous%20icefall.%20They%20find%20the%20safest%20route%20through%20it%2C%20laying%20ropes%20and%20ladders%20along%20the%20way%20to%20help%20people%20navigate%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverest-photos-show-reality-of-climb-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecliffs%20and%20crevasses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20Icefall%20Doctors%20repeatedly%20encountered%20dangers%20that%20slowed%20their%20process.%20Insufficient%20winter%20snowfall%20and%20high%20temperatures%20destabilized%20ice%20towers%20and%20bridges%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20re-evaluate%20their%20route%20several%20times%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outsideonline.com%2Foutdoor-adventure%2Feverest%2Fmount-everest-delay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOutside%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20up%20there%20one%20part%20of%20the%20day%20and%20coming%20down%20the%20next%20day%20could%20look%20very%20different.%20And%20the%20probability%20of%20that%20getting%20worse%20with%20a%20warmer%20climate%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayewski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EClimate%20change%20is%20messing%20with%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khumbu%20Icefall%20photographed%20from%20below%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663537f40dfb1341e9028b5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20global%20temperatures%20rise%2C%20melting%20ice%20is%20making%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20even%20more%20unstable.%3Cp%3EJason%20Maehl%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremains-of-long-lost-people-discovered-as-glaciers-melt-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERapid%20melting%20causes%20glaciers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20the%20Khumbu%20Glacier%2C%20to%20shrink%20and%20erode.%20In%20turn%2C%20this%20leads%20to%20more%20lakes%20and%20streams%2C%20but%20on%20a%20more%20dangerous%20level%20it%20also%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20avalanches%2C%20ice%20falls%2C%20and%20crevasses%2C%20Mayewski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20likelihood%20of%20that%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbefore-and-after-pictures-of-glaciers-melting-2014-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworse%20in%20a%20warmer%20climate%3C%2Fa%3E%20increases%20because%20ice%20becomes%20more%20mobile%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20warmer%20it%20is%2C%20the%20more%20flowing%20water.%20And%20that%20flowing%20water%20obviously%20destabilizes%20the%20ice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMayewski's%20research%20suggests%20that%20conditions%20are%20changing%20all%20over%20Mount%20Everest%2C%20not%20just%20in%20this%20region.%20His%20study%20of%20the%20South%20Col%2C%20Everest's%20highest%20glacier%2C%20revealed%20that%20one-third%20of%20its%20ice%20has%20disappeared%20in%20the%20last%20two%20to%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20just%20walking%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasecamp-strategy-mike-reid-when-democrats-turn-out-burnout-sham-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebase%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20very%20obvious%20that%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20melting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThese%20aren't%20the%20only%20dangers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mountaineer%20stepping%20over%20a%20small%20crevasse%20across%20snow-covered%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20on%20Mt.%20Everest%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66353de70dfb1341e9028f92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20have%20a%20far%20greater%20chance%20of%20dying%20from%20mountain%20sickness%20on%20Everest%20than%20falling%20into%20a%20crevasse.%3Cp%3EJason%20Maehl%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20clear%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20making%20conditions%20in%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%20more%20dangerous%2C%20not%20all%20risks%20on%20Mount%20Everest%20are%20related%20to%20climate%2C%20Arnette%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20deadliest%20climbing%20year%20in%20Mt.%20Everset's%20history%2C%2015%20of%20the%2018%20total%20deaths%20were%20caused%20by%20acute%20mountain%20sickness%2C%20falls%2C%20and%20disappearances.%20He%20feels%20that%20most%20of%20these%20deaths%20were%20likely%20preventable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20acute%20mountain%20sickness%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mild%20form%20of%20altitude%20sickness%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20treated%20if%20climbers%20and%20their%20guides%20recognize%20the%20symptoms%20quickly%20and%20get%20to%20lower%20elevation%2C%20Arnette%20said.%20But%20if%20climbers%20choose%20to%20keep%20going%2C%20their%20condition%20can%20turn%20deadly.%20AMS%20claimed%20eight%20lives%20on%20Everest%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Himalayan%20Database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnette%20believes%20that%20introducing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-some-sherpas-say-no-more-everest-guides-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20safety%20enforcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20mountain%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20to%20reduce%20fatalities.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClimbers%20sometimes%20put%20themselves%20at%20risk%20too%2C%20by%20opting%20for%20low-cost%20operators%2C%20tackling%20Everest%20without%20enough%20climbing%20experience%2C%20or%20refusing%20to%20turn%20back%20even%20when%20showing%20signs%20of%20illness.%20In%20that%20last%20case%2C%20Sherpas%20often%20have%20difficulty%20convincing%20their%20clients%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel%20due%20to%20language%20and%20cultural%20barriers%2C%20Arnette%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20added%20risks%20driven%20by%20climate%20change%20make%20climbing%20Everest%20impossible%20one%20day%3F%20Mayewski%20doesn't%20think%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20people%20still%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it%3F%20Yeah%2C%20I%20think%20they%20will.%20Will%20it%20be%20more%20dangerous%3F%20Arguably%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20already%20pretty%20dangerous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmt-everest-deadly-khumbu-icefall-grows-more-treacherous-climate-change-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714821841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66352e8f0dfb1341e9028090%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmt-everest-deadly-khumbu-icefall-grows-more-treacherous-climate-change-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20Mount%20Everest's%20deadliest%20passages%2C%20the%20Khumbu%20Icefall%2C%20delayed%20this%20year's%20climbing%20season%20by%20nearly%202%20weeks%20and%20will%20only%20get%20worse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellyn%20Lapointe)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid