0getting%20here%2C%20though%2C%20was%20a%20challenge%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20the%20scaling-Everest-like%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3Eefforts%20it%20took%20to%20achieve%20a%20successful%20pregnancy%2C%20but%2C%20when%20it%20finally%20happened%2C%20contending%20with%20what%20felt%20like%20parental%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fimposter-syndrome%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimposter%20syndrome%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuman%20nature%20being%20as%20it%20is%2C%20once%20I%20was%20pregnant%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20a%20future%20without%20a%20child%20receded%2C%20it%20was%20soon%20replaced%20with%20another%20anxiety%3A%20I%20was%20about%20to%20be%20the%20oldest%20mom%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20and%20playgrounds%20are%20notoriously%20rough-and-tumble%20territory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20unease%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-an-older-parent-pros-cons-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecoming%20an%20older%20parent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20manifested%20in%20efforts%20to%20hide%20my%20growing%20belly%20and%20my%20age%20%E2%80%94%20wearing%20the%20baggiest%20outfits%20and%20sharing%20my%20birthdate%20under%20my%20breath%20at%20ultrasound%20appointments.%20I%20fought%20a%20constant%20need%20to%20justify%20myself%2C%20wishing%20I%20had%20a%20T-shirt%20that%20succinctly%20explained%20the%20how%20and%20why%20of%20my%20pregnancy.%20I%20ruminated%20over%20whether%20showing%20up%20pregnant%20and%20single%20to%20my%20Catholic%20high%20school's%2030-year%20reunion%20would%20be%20more%20or%20less%20shocking%20than%20had%20I%20shown%20up%20pregnant%20at%20graduation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20after%20my%20sixth%20month%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20something%20changed.%20I%20was%20