%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20few%20months%20after%20my%20ex-husband%20and%20I%20separated%2C%20I%20joined%20a%20dating%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20was%20surprised%20when%20I%20quickly%20met%20someone%20I%20was%20excited%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20introduced%20him%20to%20my%20son%20fairly%20quickly%2C%20and%20if%20I%20was%20single%20again%2C%20I%20might%20do%20it%20differently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20officially%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorce-healed-family-estrangement-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseparated%20from%20my%20ex-husband%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20March%202020%20and%20took%20full%20advantage%20of%20that%20confusing%20time%20period%20to%20take%20the%20time%20to%20really%20get%20to%20know%20myself.%20I'd%20gotten%20married%20at%2023%20years%20old%20with%20next%20to%20no%20dating%20experience%20prior%20to%20that%20and%20suddenly%20found%20myself%2035%20and%20curious%20about%20who%20I%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20one%20was%20more%20surprised%20than%20I%20was%20when%20I%20met%20someone%20that%20September.%20I%20had%20jumped%20on%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-deleted-hinge-raya-tinder-bumble-oversaturated-bad-matches-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edating%20app%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20encouragement%20of%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20sure%20that%20I'd%20meet%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20just%20as%20sure%20as%20I%20was%20that%20the%20experience%20would%20be%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20I'd%20give%20it%20two%20hours%2C%20I%20told%20them%2C%20and%20so%20I%20set%20a%20timer%20and%20began%20sending%20screenshot%20after%20screenshot%20of%20messages%20from%20men%20who%20wanted%20to%20meet%20up%20that%20night%2C%20who%20told%20me%20I%20would%20have%20to%20give%20up%20my%20home%20and%20move%20into%20theirs%2C%20and%20one%20memorable%20fellow%20who%20said%20I%20would%20have%20to%20quit%20horseback%20riding%20lessons%20because%20he%20was%20allergic%20(spoiler%3A%20I%20did%20not).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20met%20my%20partner%20shortly%20after%20joining%20a%20dating%20app%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20about%2010%20minutes%20to%20go%20in%20my%20experiment%2C%20I%20connected%20with%20a%20basketball%20coach%20and%20philanthropist%20that%20I%20was%20actually%20into%2C%20and%20nearly%20four%20years%20later%2C%20we%20are%20still%20together.%20He%20was%20headed%20out%20of%20the%20country%20for%20two%20months%20the%20next%20day%2C%20which%20gave%20us%20the%20time%20to%20get%20to%20know%20each%20other%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feight-minute-phone-call-challenge-improved-my-friendships-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ephone%20calls%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20texts%20without%20any%20pressure%20of%20a%20date.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20this%20was%20ideal%20%E2%80%94%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20just%20how%20much%20of%20a%20novice%20I%20was%20when%20it%20came%20to%20relationships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20he%20got%20back%20into%20town%20that%20November%2C%20we%20met%20up%20in%20person%20and%20began%20to%20spend%20several%20days%20a%20week%20together%2C%20and%20by%20January%2C%20he%20was%20staying%20over%20more%20often%20than%20not.%20We%20usually%20saw%20each%20other%20on%20the%20days%20my%20son%20was%20at%20his%20dad's%20house%2C%20but%20my%20excitement%20at%20having%20found%20someone%20who%20felt%20so%20right%20for%20me%20and%20my%20life%20quickly%20spilled%20over%20to%20excitement%20about%20introducing%20my%20then-11-year-old%20son%20to%20him%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20I%20can%20admit%20that%20I%20rushed%20things%20in%20a%20way%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20do%20again%20if%20we%20met%20now.%20I've%20only%20understood%20this%20as%20other%20friends%20have%20begun%20dating%20and%20held%20off%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-life-with-teenage-kids-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintroducing%20their%20children%20to%20their%20new%20partners%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20six%20months%2C%20a%20year%2C%20or%20even%20longer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20no%20way%20of%20knowing%20what%20it%20would%20feel%20like%20to%20believe%20someone%20was%20so%20meant%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20and%20no%20way%20of%20knowing%20that%20I%20would%20be%20so%20eager%20for%20my%20son%20to%20get%20to%20know%20this%20great%20person%2C%20too.%20In%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20I%20even%20admire%20the%20Pollyanna-esque%20spirit%20with%20which%20I%20could%20still%20approach%20the%20world%20and%20relationships%20at%20that%20time%2C%20and%20can%20find%20sweetness%20at%20the%20core%20of%20my%20intention.%20If%20you're%20in%20love%20and%20you%20have%20a%20kid%20you%20love%2C%20naturally%2C%20you%20want%20both%20of%20your%20loves%20to%20love%20each%20other%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20as%20an%20older%2C%20wiser%2C%20and%20somewhat%20more%20experienced%20mom%20and%20woman%2C%20I%20can%20understand%20why%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-not-dating-not-interested-focus-stable-home-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20parents%20wait%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20had%20spent%20over%20a%20decade%20married%20to%20one%20person%2C%20and%20was%20very%20much%20still%20in%20a%20marriage%20mindset%20when%20I%20met%20my%20partner.%20Instead%20of%20wanting%20to%20go%20out%20and%20drink%20until%202%20a.m.%20or%20get%20dressed%20up%20for%20dates%20at%20chic%20restaurants%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20family%20outings%20and%20watch%20our%20favorite%20shows%20in%20our%20pajamas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wasn't%20trying%20to%20replace%20my%20son's%20father%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20very%20involved%20in%20his%20life%20%E2%80%94%20in%20any%20capacity%2C%20but%20was%20actively%2C%20anxiously%2C%20and%20excitedly%20trying%20to%20introduce%20a%20new%20adult%20my%20son%20could%20trust%20into%20his%20life%2C%20sometimes%20I%20worry%20before%20he%20was%20really%20ready%2C%20because%20I%20love%20how%20family%20feels%20at%20its%20core%20and%20wanted%20to%20have%20that%20with%20the%20two%20of%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20might%20have%20introduced%20my%20partner%20and%20son%20more%20slowly%20if%20I%20could%20do%20it%20again%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20experts%20advise%20waiting%20six%20months%20to%20a%20year%20into%20a%20new%20relationship%20before%20introducing%20partners%20and%20children.%20Gwyneth%20Paltrow%20and%20her%20husband%20Brad%20Falchuk%20didn't%20live%20together%20until%20they%20had%20been%20married%20for%20a%20year%20because%20of%20their%20kids%2C%20something%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20could%20ever%20do%2C%20but%20years%20down%20the%20road%2C%20I%20can%20see%20the%20wisdom%20in%20something%20like%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20there%20is%20one%20change%20I%20might%20have%20made%20if%20I%20could%2C%20I%20would%20have%20gone%20a%20lot%20slower%20with%20both%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-men-without-kids-no-fathers-less-complicated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20child%20and%20my%20partner%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20introducing%20them%20to%20one%20another%20first%20over%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20time%20first%20by%20talking%20about%20them%20to%20each%20other%2C%20then%20with%20a%20meet-up%20at%20a%20park%20or%20anime%20store%2C%20then%20maybe%20family%20dinners%20that%20eventually%20lead%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20same%20house%20together%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E