%22Karnataka%20Asks%20CBI%20To%20Seek%20Other%20Nations'%20Help%20To%20Trace%20Prajwal%20Revanna%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20government%20has%20urged%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20seek%20other%20nations%20help%20to%20trace%20JDS%20leader%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20allegedly%20raping%20multiple%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanna%2C%20the%20grandson%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20left%20the%20country%20after%20videos%20showing%20him%20allegedly%20harassing%20women%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%2C%20triggering%20a%20huge%20row%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20wrote%20to%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20extend%20all%20possible%20help%20to%20the%20victims%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20you%20to%20kindly%20extend%20all%20possible%20support%20to%20the%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scandal%20involves%20explicit%20videos%20that%20were%20allegedly%20shot%20by%20the%20MP%20and%20were%20circulated%20widely%20in%20the%20Hassan%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20up%20by%20a%20woman%20filing%20a%20police%20case%20against%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20She%20alleged%20she%20had%20been%20sexually%20abused%20multiple%20times%20between%202019%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20also%20claimed%20that%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20misbehaved%20with%20her%20daughter%20over%20a%20video%20call%20and%20had%20%26quot%3Bvulgar%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714818060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F61chqhm_prajwal-revanna_650x400_29_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-asks-cbi-to-seek-help-from-other-nations-to-trace-prajwal-revanna-accused-in-obscene-videos-case-5586979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20government%20has%20urged%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20seek%20other%20nations%20help%20to%20trace%20JDS%20leader%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20allegedly%20raping%20multiple%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-asks-cbi-to-seek-help-from-other-nations-to-trace-prajwal-revanna-accused-in-obscene-videos-case-5586979%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-asks-cbi-to-seek-help-from-other-nations-to-trace-prajwal-revanna-accused-in-obscene-videos-case-5586979%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-asks-cbi-to-seek-help-from-other-nations-to-trace-prajwal-revanna-accused-in-obscene-videos-case-5586979%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20'Shatranj'%20Move%20In%20Raebareli%20-%20Masterstroke%20Or%20Blunder%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20described%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20'shatir'%20(expert)%20'%3Cem%3Eshatranj%20ke%20khiladi%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(chess%20player)%20while%20announcing%20the%20party's%20decision%20to%20field%20him%20from%20Raebareli.%20The%20decision%20to%20forego%20Amethi%20and%20opt%20for%20Raebareli%20is%20being%20projected%20as%20the%20masterstroke%20of%20a%20grandmaster.%20Raebareli%2C%20which%20elected%20his%20grandfather%2C%20grandmother%2C%20and%20mother%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20several%20terms%20since%201952%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20safe%20bet%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20compared%20to%20neighbouring%20Amethi%2C%20where%20he%20lost%20to%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019%20after%20being%20its%20MP%20for%20three%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShatranj%20Ke%20Khiladi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%201924%20vintage%20short%20story%20by%20Munshi%20Premchand%2C%20portrays%20the%2019th%20century's%20decadent%20feudalism%20in%20Awadh%20(Raebareli%20is%20in%20the%20Awadh%20region).%20In%201977%2C%20the%20year%20Raj%20Narain%20defeated%20Indira%20Gandhi%20at%20Raebareli%2C%20maestro%20Satyajit%20Ray%20produced%20an%20epic%20movie%20based%20on%20the%20story.%20The%20film%20was%20shot%20in%20Lucknow%20while%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20on%3B%20it%20was%20released%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20state%20of%20the%20elite%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20is%20perhaps%20reflected%20in%20Premchand's%20story%2C%20which%20showed%20how%20the%20upper%20strata%20of%20Awadh%20was%20extremely%20self-centred%2C%20oblivious%20of%20the%20reality%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20centred%20around%20two%20Nawabs%20of%20Lucknow%20who%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20checkmating%20each%20other%20while%20the%20British%20took%20over%20the%20reins.%20The%20self-destruction%20of%20the%20ruling%20class%20was%20poignantly%20portrayed%20by%20Premchand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eleventh-hour%20announcement%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20candidature%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%203%20ended%20speculation%20over%20the%20prospect%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20entering%20the%20poll%20fray.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20she%20herself%20was%20not%20keen%20to%20contest.%20Her%20husband%20Robert%20Vadra%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20throw%20in%20his%20hat%20more%20than%20once%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20insisting%20it%20was%20popular%20demand%20that%20he%20should%20contest.%20The%20Congress%20never%20commented%20on%20his%20claims.%20On%20May%203%2C%20Vadra%20accompanied%20his%20wife%20to%20Raebareli%20and%20was%20a%20prominent%20face%20of%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20entourage%2C%20which%20included%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20too%20was%20present.%20No%20prominent%20face%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20accompanied%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20when%20he%20filed%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dominant%20ally%20of%20the%20bloc%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%2C%20and%20its%20workers%20welcomed%20Rahul%20but%20its%20representative%20was%20absent%20when%20he%20filed%20his%20papers%2C%20unlike%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20(IUML)%2C%20who%20had%20accompanied%20him%20in%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Wayanad%2C%20Congress%20had%20requested%20IUML%2C%20whose%20flag%20resembles%20Pakistan's%20flag%2C%20to%20keep%20its%20standard%20away%20from%20the%20pre-nomination%20road%20show.%20On%20IUML's%20insistence%2C%20Congress%20flags%20were%20also%20kept%20away.%20Both%20Congress%20and%20SP%20flags%20were%20displayed%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20though%20there%20was%20no%20road%20show.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20on%20whose%20insistence%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20entered%20the%20contest%20from%20UP%2C%20was%20busy%20campaigning%20elsewhere.%20More%20than%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20is%20keen%20on%20projecting%20his%20PDA%20(Pichhda-Dalit%20Alliance).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20gibe%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20shied%20away%20from%20Amethi%2C%20where%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20former%20confectionary%20shop%20owner%20from%20Ludhiana%20who%20had%20been%20a%20constituency%20manager%20in%20Amethi-Raebareli%20for%20four%20decades%2C%20has%20been%20fielded.%20Addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Bengal's%20Bardhaman%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20echoing%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20clarion%2C%20%26quot%3BDaro%20mat%20(don't%20be%20scared)%26quot%3B%2C%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBhago%20mat%20(don't%20scoot)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20Sharma%20can%20be%20viewed%20from%20two%20perspectives.%20One%2C%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20rewards%20its%20loyalists.%20Perhaps%20the%20relevant%20perspective%20is%20that%20after%20three%20jolts-in%20Ahmadabad%20East%2C%20Surat%2C%20and%20Indore%20-%20where%20party%20candidates%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20making%20the%20contest%20irrelevant%2C%20Sharma%20was%20the%20safest%20bet.%20Apparently%2C%20no%20prominent%20reliable%20face%20was%20available%20within%20the%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20be%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20unseating%20Rahul's%20bete%20noire%2C%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20legendary%20aloofness%20was%20all%20too%20apparent.%20Usually%2C%20a%20prominent%20candidate%20approaches%20the%20Returning%20Officer's%20podium%20to%20file%20his%20papers%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20posse%20of%20local%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20national%20faces%20and%20a%20lawyer.%20Rahul%20abruptly%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20podium%20and%20handed%20in%20his%20nomination.%20Then%20he%20looked%20around%20to%20find%20that%20his%20team%20was%20nowhere.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20slowly%20walked%20up%2C%20followed%20by%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20who%20was%20helped%20by%20Robert%20Vadra.%20Priyanka%20made%20up%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team.%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20was%20kept%20away.%20So%20were%20leaders%20of%20the%20UP%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20usually%20prolific%20in%20his%20jibes%20at%20the%20BJP%20while%20interacting%20with%20the%20media%2C%20avoided%20the%20Press%20altogether.%20He%20did%20not%20issue%20a%20statement%20explaining%20why%20he%20had%20opted%20for%20Rae%20Bareli%20while%20abandoning%20Amethi.%20He%20didn't%20visit%20Amethi%20even%20once%20after%20the%202019%20shock.%20He%20flew%20off%20to%20Pune%20after%20filing%20his%20papers.%20Priyanka%20handled%20the%20media%20in%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Wayanad%2C%20Rahul%20had%20described%20the%20constituency%20as%20his%20'home'.%20His%20candidature%20from%20Raebareli%20has%20caused%20distress%20in%20the%20Kerala%20constituency%2C%20which%20voted%20on%20April%2026.%20Voters%20there%20may%20wonder%20if%20the%20MP%20they%20elected%20in%202019%20-%20even%20as%20he%20lost%20Amethi%20-%20will%20remain%20with%20them%20if%20he%20wins%20both%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul's%20nomination%20from%20Raebareli%20after%20he%20had%20finished%20with%20his%20Wayanad%20campaign%20shows%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision%20of%20a%20seven-phase%20election%20may%20not%20have%20been%20skewed%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Opposition%20after%20all.%20The%20phase-wise%20schedule%20enabled%20Rahul%2C%20the%20only%20candidate%20who%20is%20contesting%20two%20seats%20in%202024%2C%20to%20campaign%20in%20Wayanad%20as%20a%20'local'%20and%20then%20seek%20votes%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20where%20nominations%20began%20after%20polling%20ended%20in%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20party's%20intransigence%20is%20writ%20large%20in%20the%20Raebareli%20saga.%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20said%20the%20party%20will%20have%20a%20'surprise'%20candidate%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20the%20lone%20UP%20seat%20won%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%202019.%20With%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20opting%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20from%20Rajasthan%20in%20view%20of%20her%20health%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20Gandhi%20representing%20the%20family%20bastion%20had%20reverberated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJairam%20Ramesh%2C%20while%20swatting%20away%20questions%20on%20Priyanka%20not%20contesting%2C%20said%20she%20was%20needed%20to%20campaign%20elsewhere.%20Priyanka%20has%20undoubtedly%20emerged%20as%20Congress%20party's%20star%20campaigner%2C%20who%20replies%20to%20every%20fusillade%20of%20the%20BJP%20with%20alacrity.%20However%2C%20her%20assertion%20on%20May%203%20at%20Amethi%20that%20she%20will%20move%20in%20along%20with%20'her%20family'%20to%20this%20region%20from%20May%206%20to%20campaign%20for%20Sharma%20puts%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20Jairam%20Ramesh's%20assertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20after%20the%20other%2C%20half%20a%20dozen%20spokespersons%20of%20Congress%20have%20deserted%20ship%20in%20recent%20days.%20Rohan%20Gupta%20did%20so%20after%20being%20nominated%20as%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%20from%20Ahmedabad%20East.%20Gaurabh%20Ballabh%2C%20a%20former%20Professor%20of%20the%20niche%20Xavier%20Labour%20Research%20Institute%20(XLRI)%20Jamshedpur%2C%20has%20been%20carrying%20many%20tales%20about%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20media%20since%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20One%20story%20is%20that%20on%20March%2029%2C%202014%2C%20after%20the%20BJP%20swept%20the%20sweepstakes%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20had%20said%20that%20a%20leader%20ought%20to%20retire%20on%20reaching%20the%20age%20of%2070.%20He%20turned%2070%20on%20April%209%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampaigning%20for%202024%20enters%20its%20final%20phase%20now.%20Attrition%20from%20Congress%20and%20accretion%20to%20BJP%20ranks%20has%20marked%20this%20election.%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20Rahul's%20BJP%20rival%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20was%20a%20prominent%20Congress%20face%20in%20the%20region%20till%202018.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20he%20contested%20from%20the%20BJP%20against%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20reducing%20her%20traditional%20victory%20margin%20substantially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20Raebareli%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20masterstroke%20by%20some.%20The%20ramifications%20for%20both%20Raebareli%20and%20Wayanad%20after%20the%20results%20are%20announced%20on%20June%204%20will%20have%20a%20far-reaching%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714817520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F7hrdg4qo_rahul-gandhi_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahul-gandhi-shatranj-move-in-raebareli-masterstroke-or-blunder-5587013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20