3A%22Paris%202024%20Olympics%3A%20Packages%20Offer%20Lifetime%20Experiences%20At%20Rs%204%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWe're%20used%20to%20travel%20deals%20saving%20us%20money%2C%20but%20one%20new%20package%20is%20grabbing%20headlines%20for%20its%20extravagant%20price%20tag.%20This%20isn't%20your%20typical%20vacation%20offer%3B%20it's%20all%20about%20an%20exclusive%2C%20high-end%20event%3A%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fsport%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fmay%2F04%2Fsuper-rich-exclusive-paris-olympics-packages%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMembers%2520of%2520the%2520global%2520super%2Cpart%2520of%2520the%2520opening%2520ceremony%25E2%2580%259D.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20from%20the%20global%20elite%20are%20investing%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%20(approximately%20Rs%204%2C16%2C90925)%20in%20%26quot%3Bultra-exclusive%26quot%3B%20packages%20for%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics.%20These%20packages%20purportedly%20offer%20opportunities%20such%20as%20interacting%20with%20athletes%2C%20exclusive%20access%20to%20the%20athletes'%20village%2C%20and%20the%20prospect%20of%20participating%20in%20the%20opening%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuxury%20experience%20company%20GR8%20Experience%2C%20co-owned%20by%20business%20associates%20of%20LeBron%20James%20and%20Rafael%20Nadal%2C%20is%20making%20headlines%20for%20its%20outrageously%20expensive%20Olympic%20package%20deals.%20For%20a%20cool%20%24381%2C600%2C%20you%20can%20snag%20tickets%20to%2014%20top%20events%2C%20including%20the%20coveted%20men's%20100-metre%20finals%20and%20the%20opening%20ceremony.%20But%20that's%20just%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGR8%20Experience%20promises%20%26quot%3Bmoney-can't-buy%20experiences%26quot%3B%20to%20match%20the%20price%20tag.%20Imagine%20rubbing%20shoulders%20with%20Olympic%20champions%20at%20exclusive%20meet-and-greets%2C%20or%20getting%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20peek%20at%