0arrange%20funds%20through%20crowd-funding.%20She%20shared%20a%20UPI%20QR%20code%20and%20other%20account%20details%20on%20her%20social%20media%20account%20seeking%20donations%20to%20contest%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20remains%20a%20loyal%20worker%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20had%20to%20take%20the%20drastic%20step%20as%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20raise%20enough%20funds%20on%20her%20own%20and%20the%20party%20was%20not%20giving%20her%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mohanty%20was%20also%20unhappy%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20for%20seven%20Assembly%20segments%20under%20the%20Puri%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20and%20had%20reportedly%20requested%20party%20seniors%20to%20change%20the%20candidates%20in%20some%20of%20the%20seats.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20didn't%20pay%20heed%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20in%20Puri%20will%20be%20held%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20party%20has%20already%20lost%20candidates%20in%20Surat%20and%20Indore.%20On%20April%2022%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Mukesh%20Dalal%20was%20declared%20the%20unopposed%20winner%20for%20the%20Surat%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20after%20the%20Congress%20nominee%20Nilesh%20Kumbhani%20was%20disqualified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshay%20Bam%2C%20who%20the%20Congress%20fielded%20from%20Indore%2C%20pulled%20back%20his%20name%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714815120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fost0c08c_sucharita-mohanty_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-congress-red-faced-after-puri-candidate-sucharita-mohanty-drops-out-cites-lack-of-funds-5586793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20today%20lost%20its%20third%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidate%2C%20just%20days%20before%20voting%20on%20the%20seat.%20Sucharita%20Mohanty%2C%20the%20party's%20candidate%20dropped%20out%20c