%26quot%3BAre%20Hardik%2C%20David%20That%20Bad%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Sehwag%20Fumes%20At%20MI%2C%20Demands%20Serious%20Actions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virender%20Sehwag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F86-virender-sehwag-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirender%20Sehwag%3C%2Fa%3E%20questioned%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)'s%20tactics%20during%20the%2024-run%20defeat%20to%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20their%20IPL%202024%20match%20on%20Friday.%20Chasing%20a%20below-par%20170%2C%20Mumbai%20lost%20wickets%20at%20regular%20intervals%20and%20were%20eventually%20bowled%20out%20for%20145%20off%2018.5%20overs%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium.%20While%20analysing%20the%20match%2C%20Sehwag%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bbaffled%26quot%3B%20with%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tim%20David%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F111686-tim-david-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETim%20David%3C%2Fa%3E%20arriving%20at%20No.7%20and%208%20in%20the%20lineup%2C%20respectively.%20Sehwag%20also%20posed%20a%20similar%20question%20for%20KKR%20after%20star%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Andre%20Russell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1536-andre-russell-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAndre%20Russell%3C%2Fa%3E%20batted%20down%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKKR%20saved%20Andre%20Russell%3B%20he%20played%20only%20two%20balls.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20saved%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Tim%20David.%20What%20did%20you%20achieve%20by%20doing%20that%3F%20There%20were%20many%20deliveries%20left%2C%20and%20they%20all%20got%20out.%20You%20could've%20come%20earlier%2C%20or%20maybe%20you%20could've%20finished%20the%20game%20earlier%2C%20too.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20happens%20to%20them%20when%20they%20chase...%20Hardik%20Pandya%20at%20seven%20and%20Tim%20David%20at%208.%20I%20just%20don't%20understand%20what%20they%20did.%20Are%20these%20players%20that%20bad%20that%20they%20will%20get%20out%20if%20they%20come%20earlier%3F%26quot%3B%20Sehwag%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQTBz80D05HQ%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESehwag%20also%20slammed%20Hardik%20for%20batting%20down%20the%20order%20for%20MI%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20all-rounder%20used%20to%20bat%20in%20the%20top%20order%20for%20Gujarat%20Titans.%20He%C2%A0added%20that%20the%20MI%20owners%20should%20take%20serious%20actions%20against%20the%20players%20and%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHardik%20Pandya%20batted%20at%204%20consistently%20when%20he%20was%20the%20GT%20captain.%20What%20has%20happened%20here%3F%20It%20baffles%20me%20that%20the%20experienced%20players%20are%20coming%20so%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20baffled%20by%20this.%20Management%20needs%20to%20take%20severe%20action%20on%20players%20and%20ask%20them%20what's%20happening.%20Or%2C%20players%20should%20speak%20up%20about%20why%20their%20batting%20positions%20are%20changed.%20The%20captain%2C%20batting%20coach%2C%20bowling%20coach%2C%20and%20support%20staff%20are%20at%20fault%20here.%20Owners%20need%20to%20ask%20strict%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20loss%2C%20Hardik%20said%20after%20the%20game%20that%20his%20team%20failed%20to%20form%20any%20needed%20partnerships%2C%20and%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20that%20will%20take%20time%20to%20answer%2C%20but%20he%20has%20not%20much%20to%20say%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%20obviously%20in%20the%20batting%20inning%2C%20we%20couldn't%20form%20partnerships%20and%20kept%20losing%20wickets%2C%20in%20T20s%20if%20you%20don't%20form%20partnerships%2C%20it%20will%20cost%20you.%20Not%20much%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20that%20will%20take%20some%20time%20to%20answer%20but%20for%20now%2C%20not%20much%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said%20in%20a%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714813680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F8ep0jt6_hardik-pandya-tim-david-bcci_625x300_04_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fare-hardik-pandya-tim-david-that-bad-virender-sehwag-fumes-at-mi-demands-serious-actions-5585444%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virender%20Sehwag%20questioned%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)'s%20tactics%20during%20the%2024-run%20defeat%20to%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20in%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brazil's%20Lula%20invites%20Japan's%20prime%20minister%20to%20eat%20his%20country's%20meat%2C%20and%20become%20a%20believer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714813561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109836702%2Cimgsize-649059.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fbrazils-lula-invites-japans-prime-minister-to-eat-his-countrys-meat-and-become-a-believer%2Farticleshow%2F109836609.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109836609.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBrazil's%20president%20Luiz%20In%C3%A1cio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20on%20Friday%20welcomed%20Japan's%20prime%20minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20on%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20country%2C%20with%20the%20two%20meeting%20in%20the%20capital%20of%20Brasilia%20and%20the%20South%20American%20leader%20pushing%20his%20counterpart%20to%20buy%20his%20country's%20beef.%20Brazil%20had%20wished%20to%20seize%20on%20the%20bilateral%20meeting%20t