ing%20tricky%20totals.%20The%20out-of-form%20Pandya's%20inclusion%20in%20the%2015-member%20India%20squad%20raised%20eyebrows%20but%20the%20selectors%20went%20by%20his%20past%20record%20and%20his%20ability%20to%20quickly%20change%20the%20complexion%20of%20a%20game%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball.%20If%20his%20selection%20in%20the%20squad%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20many%20were%20surprised%20by%20his%20appointment%20as%20vice-captain%20for%20the%20ICC%20showpiece%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Sreesanth%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20best%20outswing%20bowlers%20in%20the%20post-Kapil%20Dev%20era%2C%20supported%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20what%20he%20can%20do%20on%20the%20field%20minus%20this%20year's%20IPL.%20The%20way%20he's%20been%20batting%20and%20the%20way%20he's%20been%20bowling%2C%20for%20the%20country%2C%20he%20even%20led%20the%20country%20in%20one%20series%20and%20we%20won%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20remarked%20during%20a%20discussion%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20asked%20to%20Rohit%20about%20that%20and%20he%20said%20sometimes%20I'm%20the%20captain%20and%20sometimes%20I'm%20not.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20change%20the%20team's%20aura%20and%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20one%20good%20thing%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya%20comes%20in%20and%20bats%2C%20especially%20when%20he's%20chasing%20and%20Virat%20is%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20I%20think%20the%20combination%20they%20create%20is%20great.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya's%20last%20appearance%20for%20India%20came%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recovered%20from%20an%20ankle%20injury%20well%20in%20time%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202024%20and%20was%20named%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20five-time%20champions%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20place%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20--%20a%20move%20that%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Pandya's%20bowling%2C%20Sreesanth%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHardik%20can%20take%20the%20new%20ball%20or%20the%20old%20ball%2C%20especially%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20only%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20play%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it's%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Hardik%20to%20forget%20what%20he's%20done%20in%20this%20IPL%20and%20maybe%2C%20you%20never%20know%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20matches%20left%20and%20he%20may%20just%20come%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australia%20all-rounder%20Tom%20Moody%20also%20supported%20Pandya's%20selection%20in%20the%20Rohit-led%20team%2C%20saying%20he%20currently%20stands%20head%20and%20shoulders%20above%20other%20contenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BName%20me%20three%20other%20people%20who%20can%20do%20what%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20doing.%20That's%20the%20bottom%20line.%20That%20skill%20of%20being%20a%20genuine%20all-rounder%20who%20can%20bat%20in%20your%20top%20six%20and%20potentially%20bowl%20four%20overs%20for%20you%20is%20very%20rare%20in%20India%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20others%20that%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20and%20are%20okay%2C%20but%20not%20in%20international%20cricket%2C%20which%20is%20of%20a%20different%20standard.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20he%20stands%20head%20and%20shoulders%20above%20anyone%20who%20is%20competing%20for%20that%20particular%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20(chief%20selector)%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20has%20recognised%20that%20that%20is%20the%20case%20and%20we%20have%20to%20give%20him%20a%20longer%20rope%20with%20regards%20to%20his%20recovery%2C%20with%20regards%20to%20his%20form%2C%20and%20everything%20else%2C%20because%20he%20is%20a%20very%20precious%20commodity%20in%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Moody%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aussie%20also%20s