20remove%20leaves%20where%20they%20lay%20eggs.%20I%20have%20also%20used%20sticky%20fly%20traps%20to%20control%20fruit%20flies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Know%20when%20to%20prune%20trees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20keep%20getting%20good%20yields%2C%20Jayanti%20advises%20urban%20gardeners%20to%20keep%20pruning%20trees%20every%20two%20to%20three%20years.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20avoid%20pruning%2C%20then%20you%E2%80%99ll%20start%20getting%20fruits%20that%20are%20smaller%20in%20size.%20Pruning%20helps%20maintain%20tree%20size%20and%20maximise%20fruit%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Provide%20additional%20nutrients%20for%20rootbound%20trees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20three%20to%20four%20years%2C%20urban%20gardeners%20should%20dig%20out%20a%20thick%20layer%20of%20soil%20(say%203-4%20inches)%20and%20replace%20it%20with%20cow%20dung%20compost%2C%20bonemeal%2C%20and%20neem%20%3Cem%3Ekhali%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder.%20Place%20a%20thin%20layer%20of%20soil%20above%20this%20and%20then%20water%20the%20soil.%20This%20will%20help%20you%20get%20good-sized%20fruits%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%E2%80%99s%20techniques%20have%20helped%20her%20get%20sufficient%20fruits%20for%20the%20past%20three%20decades.%20She%20now%20eagerly%20awaits%20to%20harvest%20mangoes%20from%20her%20garden!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20homemaker%2C%20gardening%20is%20more%20than%20a%20fun%20hobby.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20brings%20me%20immense%20mental%20peace%20and%20contentment.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20my%20everyday%20routine.%20My%20entire%20day%20goes%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20their%20nutrients%20and%20protecting%20them%20from%20diseases%20and%20pests.%20I%20raise%20these%20trees%20like%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Jayanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Jayanti%20Sahoo.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2F