nd%20and%20wood%20is%20sourced%20from%20demolished%20homes%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Much%20of%20the%20old%20house%20has%20been%20preserved%20to%20give%20the%20home%20a%20touch%20of%20vintage%20magic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-1229x1536.jpg%201229w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG1_11zon-1713415861.jpg%201440w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347590%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMuch%20of%20the%20old%20house%20has%20been%20preserved%20to%20give%20the%20home%20a%20touch%20of%20vintage%20magic%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20credits%20architect%20Ajit%20Koujalgi%20of%20INTACH%20(Indian%20National%20Trust%20for%20Art%20and%20Cultural%20Heritage)%20for%20lending%20his%20expertise%20to%20see%20this%20to%20fruition.%20She%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20some%20interesting%20side%20trips%20looking%20for%20authentic%20doors%2C%20windows%2C%20and%20wooden%20beams%20to%20restore%20and%20build%20the%20property.%20It%20was%20challenging%20and%20time-consuming%20but%20mostly%20enjoyable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20Siddarth%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327062%2Fsanjay-austa-started-meena-bagh-homes-shimla-ratari-himachal-sustainable-homestay-stargazing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoal%20of%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20to%20be%20as%20historically%20accurate%20as%20possible.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20hundred%20percent%20authentic.%E2%80%9D%20With%20heritage%20becoming%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbuzzword%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20uncommon%20to%20hear%20of%20ancient%20buildings%20being%20razed%20in%20Puducherry%20to%20make%20way%20for%20brand-new%20residences.%20He%20did%20not%20want%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20architectural%20motifs%20intact%20but%20restore%20the%20place%20using%20new%20materials%20and%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20pictures%20and%20decor%20that%20you%20see%20around%20the%20place%20are%20borrowed%20from%20one%20of%20Francois%E2%80%99%20ancestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20history%20intact%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20these%20pictures%20are%20giving%20you%20a%20deja%20vu%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20explain.%20The%20facade%20of%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20film%20Life%20of%20Pi%20(2012).%20You%20might%20remember%20it%20from%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20Siddarth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20director%20and%20the%20production%20team%20of%20the%20film%20wanted%20to%20shoot%20in%20Puducherry%20and%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20us.%20The%20facade%20features%20in%20one%20of%20the%20opening%20scenes.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20photography%20team%20and%20cinematographer%20director%20stayed%20at%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20seen%20its%20share%20of%20fame.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20featured%20in%20a%20BBC%20travel%20documentary%20series%20%E2%80%98The%20Real%20Marigold%20Hotel%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20accolades%20are%20merely%20feathers%20in%20its%20cap.%20The%20real%20success%20lies%20in%20its%20restoration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20736px)%20100vw%2C%20736px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200%20year%20old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229.jpg%20736w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-500x349.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FG3-1713416229-150x105.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347592%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGratitude%20Heritage%20is%20a%20200-year-old%20home%20that%20is%20built%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20French%20and%20Tamil%20architectural%20practices%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Authentic%20South%20Indian%20food%20is%20served%20at%20the%20homestay%20prepared%20by%20staff%20who%20are%20locals%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FPhoto-from-Siddarth6-1713416385.jpg%20960w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347593%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAuthentic%20South%20Indian%20food%20is%20served%20at%20the%20homestay%20and%20prepared%20by%20staff%20who%20are%20locals%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Siddarth%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20features%20old%20wood%20that%20was%20collected%20from%20homes%20being%20demolished%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20An%20interesting%20thing%20to%20note%20is%20that%20the%20home%20features%20%E2%80%98Madras%20terracing%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20novel%20kind%20of%20terracing%20where%20the%20artisan%20employs%20his%20hands%20and%20feet%20to%20assemble%20the%20bricks.%20With%20modern%20techniques%20substituting%20this%20traditional%20craftsmanship%2C%20sourcing%20artisans%20was%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%2C%20Siddarth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Puducherry%2C%20we%20have%20the%20vernacular%20Tamil%20style%20of%20architecture%2C%20the%20Franco-Tamil%20style%20(that%20draws%20heavily%20from%20Chettiar%20style)%2C%20and%20then%20those%20which%20are%20predominantly%20said%20to%20be%20French%20style%20because%20of%20the%20arches%20and%20pillars%20and%20certain%20other%20details.%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20falls%20in%20the%20third%20category.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20restoration%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20care%20was%20taken%20to%20not%20upset%20anything%20of%20the%20old%20home.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20walls%20were%20broken%20and%20no%20trees%20were%20cut%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddarth%20shares.%20He%20goes%20on%20to%20narrate%20an%20anecdote%20of%20how%20a%20mango%20tree%20in%20the%20courtyard%20was%20hindering%20the%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chopping%20it%20off%2C%20they%20called%20in%20%E2%80%98tree%20doctors%E2%80%99%20who%20pulled%20the%20tree%20out%20of%20the%20way%20until%20work%20was%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jyoti%20and%20her%20son%20Siddarth%2C%20the%20duo%20behind%20the%20restoration%20and%20managing%20of%20the%20Gratitude%20Heritage%20homestay%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Ftravel-6_11zon-1713764375-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20